# Sidecar binaries for Tauri's externalBin, provisioned per target triple:
#   node-<triple>            — Node runtime (scripts/provision-node.mjs)
#   mainframe-daemon-<triple> — Rust daemon (scripts/provision-rust-daemon.mjs)
# Real binaries are MB-scale and platform-specific — never committed. cargo check
# does not need them; `tauri build` does, so provision first. Only this
# .gitignore + README.md are tracked.
node-*
mainframe-daemon-*
!.gitignore
!README.md
